                </div>
                <div class="tc-card-media">
                    <img src="/Images/methods-test-pc.jpg" alt="Quick withdrawals" />
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tc-card">
                <div class="tc-card-body">
                    <h4>Caring Customer<br />Support 24/7</h4>
                    <p>We speak English and 10+ other languages. Whatever question you might have, drop us a line.</p>
                </div>
