                    <span class="accordion-title">Weekly webinars</span>
                    <span class="accordion-indicator" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
                </button>
                <div id="acc-panel-1" class="accordion-panel" role="region" aria-labelledby="acc-btn-1" hidden>
                    <p>Learn to make a profit under the guidance of professional full-time traders — join weekly lessons in English.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-btn" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="acc-panel-2" id="acc-btn-2">
                    <span class="accordion-title">Trading Ideas</span>
                    <span class="accordion-indicator" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
                </button>
                <div id="acc-panel-2" class="accordion-panel" role="region" aria-labelledby="acc-btn-2" hidden>
                    <p>Quick, easy, and effective. Use free daily trading signals, follow instructions, and book profit.</p>
                </div>
